SacOil Denies It Published Misleading Information About Oil Block in Congo

-- B y   V e r n o n   W e s s e l s
-- 
2011-03-14T06:42:11Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-03-14/sacoil-denies-it-published-misleading-information-about-oil-block-in-congo.html
SacOil Holdings Ltd. said it denies
a complaint by shareholder Kevin van der Walt that it published
incorrect or misleading information on an oil block in the
Democratic Republic of Congo.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Vernon Wessels at 
 vwessels@bloomberg.net  